{"id": "1245086375372394616", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 19, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "补充一下，序章起名字的时候，墓碑上的4句话也是这4句。", "timestamp": "2024-05-28T18:48:44.475000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1245086374982586430", "filename": "Image_1716921979039.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 528153, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1245086374982586430/Image_1716921979039.png?ex=69ccbfcc&is=69cb6e4c&hm=5c043e42a6cc99c4fa5d04cb4c5d47b3ced39a50a86a3d13ac416651dc9cd84d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1244042094528434266", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1245087256880873533", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "【背景】办公室背景的窗户上有校徽纹样，下方绸缎上文字是：\nMISKATONIC UNIVERSITY\n密斯卡托尼克大学\n\n绸缎中间写的是1690，也就是密大建校时间。课题记录上面写的时间也是1690：https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1221527962495484015/1221578169254150255\n\n早期宣发的时候用的就是密大，后来应该是版权原因所以改成弥萨格了。", "timestamp": "2024-05-28T18:52:14.643000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-28T18:55:10.069000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1245087256042012702", "filename": "Image_1716922156690.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 735055, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1245087256042012702/Image_1716922156690.png?ex=69ccc09e&is=69cb6f1e&hm=d7a73bed7eec2f7d33dd5daa566274c13a76b2543a3b3fbc3453defb27b94f70&"}, {"id": "1245087256369299576", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-29-02-43-11-78_6b26a6c56e60a8073a58a8a51c55ef41.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 371826, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1245087256369299576/Screenshot_2024-05-29-02-43-11-78_6b26a6c56e60a8073a58a8a51c55ef41.jpg?ex=69ccc09e&is=69cb6f1e&hm=56685eaca9ca64697dd290430f0a404528c7cd17128a87b1cce499bb7564d90b&"}, {"id": "1245087256687939665", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-29-02-43-22-78_6b26a6c56e60a8073a58a8a51c55ef41.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 398610, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1245087256687939665/Screenshot_2024-05-29-02-43-22-78_6b26a6c56e60a8073a58a8a51c55ef41.jpg?ex=69ccc09e&is=69cb6f1e&hm=ab5fe0171de7ed357051104304e96173d38d41b5d71799e6c234b1fec4f375d1&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1245090057254207539", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "所以同理可得，【造物】崭新的钱包\n图片校徽下缎带上的英文也是：密斯卡托尼克1690大学", "timestamp": "2024-05-28T19:03:22.304000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1245090056905953320", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-29-03-01-23-21_40deb401b9ffe8e1df2f1cc5ba480b12.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 346422, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1245090056905953320/Screenshot_2024-05-29-03-01-23-21_40deb401b9ffe8e1df2f1cc5ba480b12.jpg?ex=69ccc33a&is=69cb71ba&hm=b517a049d67bbcff653d74906ebdd0fb9c05ae007f6b8fc3e53c6a81d4512065&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1245092100257878066", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "【背景】学校钟楼地下\n框出来的地方写了：\nEmergency Exit\n紧急出口，安全出口", "timestamp": "2024-05-28T19:11:29.394000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1245092099209035776", "filename": "Image_1716923221734.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 89914, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1245092099209035776/Image_1716923221734.jpg?ex=69ccc521&is=69cb73a1&hm=bcab1aa41acafa231f94b1b1c53ae377cca69cf25e4522b09ea8d90b96645166&"}, {"id": "1245092099741974629", "filename": "Image_1716923174263.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 439990, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1245092099741974629/Image_1716923174263.png?ex=69ccc521&is=69cb73a1&hm=12e5cdee5d51aa23cb796cbbe583c4a39d3e19042a11e483a5b24e277d5f2335&"}, {"id": "1245092100068868147", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-29-02-45-42-10_cae2e283440eaf407874acc641554250.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 324138, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1245092100068868147/Screenshot_2024-05-29-02-45-42-10_cae2e283440eaf407874acc641554250.jpg?ex=69ccc521&is=69cb73a1&hm=c72015a19cf5aae93122658ae24fe1900f3b12a120828b2712bf175fb3a06775&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1245092599837229129", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "可惜无法与【造物】安全出口，或者是学校地图对应上。", "timestamp": "2024-05-28T19:13:28.503000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-28T19:13:41.726000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1245095598345162884", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "这两张图能很清楚的看到提灯教会的标志，具体提及在https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1221527962495484015/1221533255887618259", "timestamp": "2024-05-28T19:25:23.403000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1245095596667310263", "filename": "Image_1716923995105.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 3224625, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1245095596667310263/Image_1716923995105.png?ex=69ccc863&is=69cb76e3&hm=9c9a41d6f5a44b89fd99bd5b91b9b0826d3d92c6fd48fe16b7859a632ccf1650&"}, {"id": "1245095597577601115", "filename": "Image_1716924000179.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2578125, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1245095597577601115/Image_1716924000179.png?ex=69ccc863&is=69cb76e3&hm=5f65a1035cf9f66038383355a4011748ad103d6043d751b13fd45020b9afc48c&"}, {"id": "1245095598261145763", "filename": "Image_1716924300605.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 85131, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1245095598261145763/Image_1716924300605.jpg?ex=69ccc863&is=69cb76e3&hm=92e253f0a56c31027445c27dc7f4dafb7ad566610d53f4b853c4a98873ecac0b&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1245100390152802435", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "很显然还能再补充一下，【背景】幻梦深潜（大学）\n这个很大的墓碑上的4句模糊不清的话，也已经是这4句。具体见https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1221527962495484015/1244042094528434266\n\n以大学为背景出场的唤醒体boss目前有希洛「破链者」、詹金「窜行者」和尤乌哈希「猩红」。\n大学背景图的说明是这么写的：\n「此处埋葬着一所大学，千疮百孔，疲惫不堪\n它曾为人类存续奉献了一点希望与勇气\n至于结果如何，你现在都看到了」\n\n所以，可能故事的结尾就是环行拉蒙娜所在的世界线那样，被融蚀侵蚀。", "timestamp": "2024-05-28T19:44:25.859000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1245100541252599849", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2024-05-28T19:45:01.884000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1245100541089157190", "filename": "Image_1716925111139.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 506434, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1245100541089157190/Image_1716925111139.png?ex=69ccccfd&is=69cb7b7d&hm=c130a7be8927a6599a7366b521a5d130c8824c7ad12dbeb6f894dc92c69ceea3&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1245101326917177476", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "【背景】地铁\n所以地下铁的门上写的就是地铁underground，门上面两边还写了大写罗马数字Ⅱ，可能是在二号车厢。", "timestamp": "2024-05-28T19:48:09.201000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1245101326510198928", "filename": "Image_1716925587871.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2757588, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1245101326510198928/Image_1716925587871.png?ex=69cccdb9&is=69cb7c39&hm=819b5ad303caa2fe709036f12da507bebd01539a6a610a3009fd8f6df3249a00&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1245103132594143325", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "【背景】罗杰斯蜡像馆\n黄色框起来的（p2）是southwork street，也就是剧情中所说的「南华克大街」。\n\n蜡像馆位于南华克大街44号。\n图中红色框起来的（p3）就是Rogers Museum，罗杰斯蜡像馆（博物馆）。", "timestamp": "2024-05-28T19:55:19.708000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1245103131420004382", "filename": "Image_1716925770582.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2251392, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1245103131420004382/Image_1716925770582.png?ex=69cccf67&is=69cb7de7&hm=d7ab13ab84d07b52f323feabca0b39a01b7be200384680049fae778420410273&"}, {"id": "1245103131872985149", "filename": "Image_1716925764686.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 432852, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1245103131872985149/Image_1716925764686.png?ex=69cccf67&is=69cb7de7&hm=b46826e4c51fab651fc83acae6d98ea774b82d1d9a124de89aeb2ac7c696f343&"}, {"id": "1245103132300546098", "filename": "Image_1716925767671.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1402837, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1245103132300546098/Image_1716925767671.png?ex=69cccf67&is=69cb7de7&hm=70f9af3ae87db374960d82f91b733ab166623246fb71c5ec57ead0c2b4a6e584&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1245121800321503302", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "【背景】伦敦东区\n几家店铺名，从左往右，p1是：\n……rie ancienne & moderne\n（图不全，但是没关系，p2有完整版本），也就是：\nlibrairie ancienne & moderne\n古代与现代书店（法语）（可能是新书旧书都卖的书店）\n\nflorists shop\n花店\nflorists本身就是英语的花店；花商的意思\n\np2\n竖着的挂牌写着：\nhotel\n酒店；旅馆；酒吧；餐馆；旅社；酒馆\n\nlibrairie ancienne\n旧书店（法语）\n\nthe tipperary\n不知道为什么有个翻译器翻成了「酒鬼」，可以因为有定冠词吧。\nTipperary是个地名，蒂珀雷里郡；蒂珀雷里，是爱尔兰南部一郡。也有同名歌曲。\n\nle bon georges\n好乔治（法语）\n图中是把文字反转了，第四家店也是同名反转店，但是在夜景开灯背景中，这个文字是正过来的，很好辨认。", "timestamp": "2024-05-28T21:09:30.441000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-28T21:27:04.131000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1245121798790578186", "filename": "Image_1716929424994.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 985358, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1245121798790578186/Image_1716929424994.png?ex=69cce0ca&is=69cb8f4a&hm=474b95e335c30915bad61e3779bafa3978f84c8e70bf024cd517907485072c88&"}, {"id": "1245121799344099379", "filename": "Image_1716929428206.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1467007, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1245121799344099379/Image_1716929428206.png?ex=69cce0ca&is=69cb8f4a&hm=1f99b8bb24bba2566eacdcada70f5054a5cc925dbf0f902ab63c68d9fcf5955b&"}, {"id": "1245121799927234662", "filename": "Image_1716929430724.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1555917, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1245121799927234662/Image_1716929430724.png?ex=69cce0ca&is=69cb8f4a&hm=2c2fc4a8a8219c915ba839dd6690e2436807af00102f523dd2c4cb05eecde83e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1245123237848023141", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "【背景】市立图书馆地下\n虽然都是地下图复用，但是上面写的英文不一样，这张图本身就模糊了很多，左边有个牌子是真的看不清，但是我猜是「安全出口」.jpg，挂铁门上的牌子写着：\nVorsichl\n注意事项（德语）", "timestamp": "2024-05-28T21:15:13.174000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1245123237965205607", "filename": "Image_1716930787102.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1402942, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1245123237965205607/Image_1716930787102.png?ex=69cce221&is=69cb90a1&hm=fd99f2ea914cdfa62f1e51685162d357ef3507a2d530e8c0d1dd082d8117e844&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1245126061591760946", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "【背景】马戏团\n墙上海报的字太抽象了，只能看清dBCU，也就大脸旁边的售票箱上的字看得清，也就是：\nticket\n票;车票;彩票;入场券;券;(商店中标明货物价格、尺码等的)标签;奖券;（交通违章）通知单，罚款单;戏票;候选人名单\n\n下面还写了5°，可能是50元？或许代表了其他意思。", "timestamp": "2024-05-28T21:26:26.407000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-28T21:27:46.401000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1245126061306675350", "filename": "Image_1716931055642.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1764101, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1245126061306675350/Image_1716931055642.png?ex=69cce4c2&is=69cb9342&hm=d421b925fa78057d2c340cd4ef0c2143c68f04502ede52ed7082423d00c43910&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1245130974195613808", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "【背景】拉伊\n白天图上是花体，糊的看不清。应该有三个单词，第三个或许最后是ing结尾。\n晚上就换了看的很清楚字体，能看到的部分是：\non the sending out of the soul\n论灵魂的发出", "timestamp": "2024-05-28T21:45:57.663000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-28T21:46:08.482000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1245130973826256957", "filename": "Image_1716931714979.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1166605, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1245130973826256957/Image_1716931714979.png?ex=69cce955&is=69cb97d5&hm=24dd04736c88b8e56ddbf8b4d1a853a4b25a6c88389b7dbb012329cc3dbf4b55&"}, {"id": "1245130974237560943", "filename": "Image_1716931718405.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 649048, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1245130974237560943/Image_1716931718405.png?ex=69cce955&is=69cb97d5&hm=56217128392cdc2d8c8e0e2d8f31216da4655dd86deb7b16b598f37c3fb1ccf9&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1245135083623546932", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "【背景】林肯高街\n从左到右：\nPaint & Hardware\n油漆和硬件\nHardware\n硬件;   (家庭及园艺用)工具，设备，五金制品;   硬件设备;   机器;   车辆;\n（应该是一家五金店）\n\n大门侧牌，白的发亮的是：\ntailor\n(尤指为顾客个别定制男装的)裁缝\n（应该是个裁缝店招牌）\n\n大门正宣传牌就是五金店Paint & Hardware\n\n上面挂了个大广告牌的是：\nkeppnteps？uceppnteps？\nxeppateps\n看不清等显微镜起床\n\n再右和正门平行的店铺名被挡住了，只能看到TED\n\n最右绿色招牌写着：\nRISIDR???\nRISTOR???\n可能是ristorante，意大利语中的餐厅。", "timestamp": "2024-05-28T22:02:17.427000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-29T08:57:44.739000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1245135083468488755", "filename": "Image_1716931707969.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1779422, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1245135083468488755/Image_1716931707969.png?ex=69cced29&is=69cb9ba9&hm=5eaa79803969d7e97c5526cda3755b166f45f2de4d194e646727b4873ec30ead&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1245135750530596886", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "左边白色挂牌写着：\nCAMBRIA\n（第一个字可能是C）坎布里亚，英国的一个郡名；或是威尔士；寒武纪。\n：在英语中，\"Cambria\"可以指代威尔士的古罗马拉丁名，也可以是北美一些地区的地名，如美国宾夕法尼亚州的Cambria County。此外，\"Cambria\"也是一个常见的品牌名和公司名。\n\n右边下面：\nTHE WOMANS F\n剩下被挡住了，可能是free之类的吧.jpg\n\n右边上面是镜像的文字：\nEL STATION\n可能是车站或其他站点\n人工智能回答：\n这个名称可能是某个车站名称的一部分，而且“el”这个词可以出现在许多不同的语言和地名中。例如，在西班牙语中，“el”是定冠词，相当于英语的“the”，所以这个“el”可能是某个西班牙语或相关语言地名的组成部分。\n如果这个车站位于英语国家，那么“el”可能是某个专有名词或地名的缩写。例如，在纽约市，地铁系统被称为“Subway”，而在芝加哥，类似的系统被称为“L”（发音为“El”），因此“el station”可能是芝加哥某个车站的简称。", "timestamp": "2024-05-28T22:04:56.430000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-28T22:19:52.398000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1245135750270418965", "filename": "Image_1716931711316.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 762210, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1245135750270418965/Image_1716931711316.png?ex=69ccedc8&is=69cb9c48&hm=b023ff93be516f69d3ae63f3ca43a529bae63cdc68d0b9ec81de0932c54ca8ca&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
